You must be able to explain some specifics about this infrastructure:
1. For every additional element, why you are adding it
   To protect Web infrastructure. 

2. What are firewalls for
   Firewalls allows, blocks, inspects incoming and outgoing network tarfic

3. Why is the traffic served over HTTPS
   HTTPS encrypts network trafic using SSL certificates.

4. What monitoring is used for
   To collect request rates, TLS handshake errors, HTTP 4xx/5xx errors,
   To alert if traffic stops or spikes.

5. How the monitoring tool is collecting data
   The monitoring tool reads log files on the server

6. Explain what to do if you want to monitor your web server QPS
   To monitor your web server's Queries Per Second (QPS), you will need to utilize specific tools and methodologies depending on your server environment. 
   The general process involves using monitoring software, analyzing log files

7. You must be able to explain what the issues are with this infrastructure:
   

8. Why terminating SSL at the load balancer level is an issue


9. Why having only one MySQL server capable of accepting writes is an issue


10. Why having servers with all the same components (database, web server and application server) might be a problem

